      <section eId="sec_CHC-874">
        <num>CHC 874</num>
        <heading>874. Â Severance of individual cases for adjudication</heading>
        <subsection eId="CHC-874__subsec_1">
          <num>(1)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The state elects to try them separately.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CHC-874__subsec_2">
          <num>(2)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The court, on motion of the child and after contradictory hearing with the district attorney, is satisfied that justice requires a severance.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
